                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6852" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">HRM-0472</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8602 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">推陈出“薪”，运“酬”制胜 ——A银行的宽带薪酬改革</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Push out of the &quot;salary&quot;, luck &quot;reward&quot; to win       --Broadband compensation reform of A Bank</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">孙莹，窦靖时，杨文琦</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中国海洋大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中国银行青岛分行</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">贸易与金融业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">人力资源部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">23 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">酬改革；薪酬矩阵；宽带薪酬；商业银行</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">ompensation reform, compensation matrix, broadband compensation, commercial bank</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例描述了A银行青岛分行的一场薪酬改革风波。A银行是我国大型国有商业银行，其分行之一坐落于青岛。该行自1986年成立以来，历经一系列薪酬改革，而公司离职率上升、员工积怨已久等问题在2021年底越发突出。领导层意识到薪酬制度体系改革迫在眉睫之后，在人力资源部经理层的总指导下，绩效与薪酬管理团队迅速调研了工资倒挂、待遇差距、城区领导薪酬区间设置不合理、宽带薪酬成长机制欠缺等现存薪酬问题，同时，管理团队高效制定了关于进一步完善薪酬体系的实施意见，明确了优化薪酬矩阵，确保多劳多得，建立薪点成长机制，完善薪酬管理机制等系统性改革。本案例重点展示了青岛分行以现存问题为导向，集思广益完善宽带薪酬体系制度实施方案的全过程。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This case describes a salary reform storm in the Qingdao Branch of Bank A. Bank A is a large state-owned commercial bank in China. One of its branches is located in Qingdao. Since its inception in a series of compensation reforms, the bank has occurred in 1986.By the end of 2021, problems include rising turnover rates and persistent employee complaints. Leadership realized that the salary system and system reform is imminent, under the guidance of human resources manager, performance and salary management team quickly investigated wages, treatment gap, urban leadership salary interval set unreasonable, broadband salary growth mechanism lack existing compensation problems, at the same time, the management team efficient opinions on further improve the compensation system, optimize compensation matrix, ensure more work, establish pay point growth mechanism, improve the salary management mechanism and other systemic reform. This case focuses on the whole process of Qingdao Branch to improve the implementation plan of the broadband compensation system based on the existing problems.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《人力资源管理》、《薪酬管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">共同富裕国家政策；薪酬收入结构改革；薪酬分配原则理论；宽带薪酬理论；宽带薪酬要素理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-12</td>
                            </tr>
